http://www.fidius.org/quiz/pirate.php

So at the end you can donate money, and I thought hey, that WAS fun. So I
donated a dollar. Here's what you get to read if you go through that, though.
The appeal and the thank-you:



Details from Shaun Salnave

fi-del'i-te: shameless begging page
Rest assured, all donations will got to feed and clothe the needy, or pay for
webhosting and CDs and electronics equipment. What! I'm needy, trust me. My
ex-girlfriends are always going on about how needy I am.

Oh most happy donor of money for my page! You are truly a soul blessed with
